Import: import { ImpersonationBanner } from '@/components/auth-impersonation-banner/impersonation-banner'

Place at the top of your layout:
<ImpersonationBanner
  impersonatedUser={{ name: 'Jane Doe', email: 'jane@example.com' }}
  adminUser={{ name: 'Admin', email: 'admin@example.com' }}
  onStopImpersonating={() => endImpersonation()}
/>

Tip: Add padding-top (pt-10 or pt-12) to your body/main content to offset the fixed banner.
